text: Bikshikovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kayrakovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 277 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Mishkino, 6 km from Kayrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Bikshikovo
